    "description": "ThumBeat: 节奏狂击版是一款短音乐、按键狂击的节奏游戏。不管用键盘、滑鼠还是游戏手把，把你的节奏暴击技巧发挥到极致<br><br>游戏特色：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790640/extras/7a45185a7c05610d9f54baeba5007a3a.avif?t=1653702631\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>原创音乐：从怀旧8-bit电玩风到民谣吉他，多种音乐风格、超过25首原创曲目<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790640/extras/281443eddb94db4f8a8c0fc8e80fc814.avif?t=1653702631\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>多种难度：从简单到爆难，每首曲目都有4种难度，看你能挑战到什么程度！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790640/extras/3fcb583a922b41c1edc5997863267f51.avif?t=1653702631\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>较劲全球：与全球玩家一较高下，用你的纪录刷新排行榜<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790640/extras/1ac04c197fe0bb8b5d9303ed6340f686.avif?t=1653702631\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>多元操作：支援键盘、滑鼠、触控萤幕、游戏手把四种游玩方式<br><br><br>- 自由挑战：想更疯狂？音乐倍速可自由调整，小心不要造成手指伤害",
